	pages viewed by other users. They can use this malicious script to force users to silently perform
	actions that benefit the attacker, like sending them their account or session credentials. Any view
	code that takes data controlled by a user and puts it on the page without validation or encoding is
	likely to be vulnerable to this attack.{{/paragraph}}

